                <p>Each individual eats every day, and the choices that we make are what will improve the climate change problems. Your diet should consist of MACROS nutrients, therefore: carbs, protein, and healthy fats. To this list, we need to add fruits and vegetables.</p>
                <p>How much of these foods you should eat depends on your goal. A healthy diet plan suggests 3 meals a day plus two snacks. You should try to keep this format of eating, then spending by your needs and changing the portion size of the foods. With the calculator above you can check the number of calories that you need in a day, to not overeat!</p>
            </div>

